                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Vibius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Anie<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>sis</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXI <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan> arbi<lb break="no" n="6"/>ter <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Larti <lb n="7"/>et <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> Mursi <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eredum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Drei aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten (Z. 1-4; teilweise stark verrieben); der übrige Teil 1676 verbrannt; Lesung ab Z. 5 nach einer Kopie von 1676. Z. 4 (Ende): Die Anzahl der Lebensjahre muss in irgendeiner Weise verschrieben sein. (B): Kovács - Prohászka (Wiedergabe eines Briefes von F. Neigebaur 1847): Z. 1: Vibios; Farkas - Gabler: Z. 4 (Ende): XXC; Kovács - Prohászka (Wiedergabe eines Briefes von F. Neigebaur 1847): Z. 5: H. S. ET. F. ARBI; Z. 7: MVRSII.</p>
            </div>
